 &lt;p class="card-text mt-1">什么是交互式 Shell&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>常见环境变量</title><link>https://kugarocks.github.io/zh-cn/linux/env/variables/</link><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 20:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://kugarocks.github.io/zh-cn/linux/env/variables/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="shell">SHELL&lt;/h2>
